dct_title_s: Le Transvaal et les régions limitrophes de l'Afrique australe
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by shading and spot heights. Includes insets of southeastern Africa and "Les routes anglaises vers l'Afrique du Sud." Includes text and ill. on verso. Historic Maps copy imperfect: cover wanting; map is unfolded.
